{
    "title": "acceptance by final state vs empty stack",
    "html": "<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark\"><p data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"210\">Yes! In a <strong data-start=\"10\" data-end=\"69\">Pushdown Automaton (PDA) with acceptance by empty stack</strong>, a string is considered <strong data-start=\"94\" data-end=\"106\">accepted</strong> if the stack becomes empty <strong data-start=\"134\" data-end=\"162\">at the end of processing</strong>—even if the PDA does not reach a final state.</p><h3 data-start=\"212\" data-end=\"257\"><strong data-start=\"216\" data-end=\"257\">Two Ways a PDA Can Accept a Language:</strong></h3><ol data-start=\"258\" data-end=\"507\"><li data-start=\"258\" data-end=\"365\"><strong data-start=\"261\" data-end=\"290\">Acceptance by Final State</strong>: The PDA must end in a designated <strong data-start=\"325\" data-end=\"340\">final state</strong> after reading the input.</li><li data-start=\"366\" data-end=\"507\"><strong data-start=\"369\" data-end=\"398\">Acceptance by Empty Stack</strong>: The PDA must <strong data-start=\"413\" data-end=\"443\">empty its stack completely</strong> when the input is fully read, regardless of the state it is in.</li></ol><p data-start=\"509\" data-end=\"629\">For <strong data-start=\"513\" data-end=\"542\">acceptance by empty stack</strong>, <strong data-start=\"544\" data-end=\"577\">a final state is not required</strong>—as long as the PDA can reach a configuration where:</p><ul data-start=\"630\" data-end=\"690\"><li data-start=\"630\" data-end=\"664\"><strong data-start=\"632\" data-end=\"663\">The input is fully consumed</strong>.</li><li data-start=\"665\" data-end=\"690\"><strong data-start=\"667\" data-end=\"689\">The stack is empty</strong>.</li></ul><hr data-start=\"692\" data-end=\"695\"><h3 data-start=\"697\" data-end=\"744\"><strong data-start=\"701\" data-end=\"744\">Example PDA with Empty Stack Acceptance</strong></h3><p data-start=\"745\" data-end=\"811\">Let's consider the language <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>L</mi><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">{</mo><msup><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><msup><mi>b</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><mo>∣</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>≥</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">}</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">L = \\{ a^n b^n \\mid n \\geq 1 \\}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">L</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">{</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">a</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.6644em;\"><span style=\"top: -3.063em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">b</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.6644em;\"><span style=\"top: -3.063em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">∣</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.7719em; vertical-align: -0.136em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">≥</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">}</span></span></span></span>.</p><p data-start=\"813\" data-end=\"884\">A PDA for this language (with empty stack acceptance) works as follows:</p><ul data-start=\"885\" data-end=\"1032\"><li data-start=\"885\" data-end=\"912\">Push <code data-start=\"892\" data-end=\"895\">a</code>s onto the stack.</li><li data-start=\"913\" data-end=\"955\">For each <code data-start=\"924\" data-end=\"927\">b</code>, pop an <code data-start=\"936\" data-end=\"939\">a</code> from the stack.</li><li data-start=\"956\" data-end=\"1032\">If the stack becomes empty <strong data-start=\"985\" data-end=\"1007\">exactly at the end</strong>, the string is accepted.</li></ul><h4 data-start=\"1034\" data-end=\"1111\"><strong data-start=\"1039\" data-end=\"1111\">Transitions (assuming input alphabet {a, b} and stack alphabet {A}):</strong></h4><ol data-start=\"1112\" data-end=\"1407\"><li data-start=\"1112\" data-end=\"1220\"><p data-start=\"1115\" data-end=\"1220\"><strong data-start=\"1115\" data-end=\"1143\">Push <code data-start=\"1122\" data-end=\"1125\">a</code>s onto the stack</strong>:<br data-start=\"1144\" data-end=\"1147\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>q</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>a</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>Z</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>→</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>q</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>Z</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">(q_0, a, Z) \\to (q_0, AZ)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3011em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0359em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">0</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">a</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.07153em;\">Z</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3011em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0359em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">0</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.07153em;\">Z</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span><br data-start=\"1181\" data-end=\"1184\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>q</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>a</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>A</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>→</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>q</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>A</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">(q_0, a, A) \\to (q_0, AA)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3011em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0359em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">0</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">a</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3011em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0359em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">0</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">AA</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></p></li><li data-start=\"1225\" data-end=\"1294\"><p data-start=\"1228\" data-end=\"1294\"><strong data-start=\"1228\" data-end=\"1248\">Pop for each <code data-start=\"1243\" data-end=\"1246\">b</code></strong>:<br data-start=\"1249\" data-end=\"1252\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>q</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>b</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>A</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>→</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>q</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>ϵ</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">(q_0, b, A) \\to (q_0, \\epsilon)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3011em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0359em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">0</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">b</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3011em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0359em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">0</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">ϵ</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></p></li><li data-start=\"1296\" data-end=\"1407\"><p data-start=\"1299\" data-end=\"1407\"><strong data-start=\"1299\" data-end=\"1333\">Accept when the stack is empty</strong>:<br data-start=\"1334\" data-end=\"1337\">If the input is fully read and the stack is empty, the PDA accepts.</p></li></ol><p data-start=\"1409\" data-end=\"1488\"><strong data-start=\"1409\" data-end=\"1437\">No final state is needed</strong>—acceptance happens <strong data-start=\"1457\" data-end=\"1487\">just by emptying the stack</strong>.</p><hr data-start=\"1490\" data-end=\"1493\"><h3 data-start=\"1495\" data-end=\"1516\"><strong data-start=\"1499\" data-end=\"1516\">Key Takeaways</strong></h3><ul data-start=\"1517\" data-end=\"1810\"><li data-start=\"1517\" data-end=\"1579\"><strong data-start=\"1519\" data-end=\"1552\">Final states are not required</strong> in empty-stack acceptance.</li><li data-start=\"1580\" data-end=\"1657\">The PDA may end in <strong data-start=\"1601\" data-end=\"1614\">any state</strong>, as long as the stack is empty at the end.</li><li data-start=\"1658\" data-end=\"1810\">This is equivalent in power to <strong data-start=\"1691\" data-end=\"1726\">PDA with final-state acceptance</strong> (both recognize context-free languages, and you can convert between the two types).</li></ul><p data-start=\"1812\" data-end=\"1877\" data-is-last-node=\"\">Would you like a proof that both acceptance types are equivalent?</p></div><div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark\"><p data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"123\">To prove that <strong data-start=\"14\" data-end=\"43\">acceptance by empty stack</strong> and <strong data-start=\"48\" data-end=\"77\">acceptance by final state</strong> are equivalent, we need to show two things:</p><ol data-start=\"125\" data-end=\"352\"><li data-start=\"125\" data-end=\"238\"><strong data-start=\"128\" data-end=\"236\">Every PDA with empty stack acceptance can be converted to an equivalent PDA with final state acceptance.</strong></li><li data-start=\"239\" data-end=\"352\"><strong data-start=\"242\" data-end=\"350\">Every PDA with final state acceptance can be converted to an equivalent PDA with empty stack acceptance.</strong></li></ol><hr data-start=\"354\" data-end=\"357\"><h2 data-start=\"359\" data-end=\"448\"><strong data-start=\"362\" data-end=\"446\">1. Converting PDA with Empty Stack Acceptance to PDA with Final State Acceptance</strong></h2><h3 data-start=\"449\" data-end=\"464\"><strong data-start=\"453\" data-end=\"462\">Idea:</strong></h3><p data-start=\"465\" data-end=\"604\">We modify the PDA so that instead of checking for an empty stack, it transitions to a <strong data-start=\"551\" data-end=\"574\">special final state</strong> when the stack becomes empty.</p><h3 data-start=\"606\" data-end=\"629\"><strong data-start=\"610\" data-end=\"627\">Construction:</strong></h3><ul data-start=\"630\" data-end=\"1177\"><li data-start=\"630\" data-end=\"723\">Let <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>Q</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Σ</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Γ</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>δ</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>q</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>Z</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P = (Q, \\Sigma, \\Gamma, \\delta, q_0, Z_0)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Q</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">Σ</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">Γ</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03785em;\">δ</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3011em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0359em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">0</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.07153em;\">Z</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3011em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0715em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">0</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span> be a PDA that accepts by empty stack.</li><li data-start=\"724\" data-end=\"770\">Introduce a new final state <strong data-start=\"754\" data-end=\"767\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>q</mi><mi>f</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">q_f</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.7167em; vertical-align: -0.2861em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3361em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0359em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right: 0.10764em;\">f</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.2861em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong>.</li><li data-start=\"771\" data-end=\"1102\">Modify the transitions to allow a transition to <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>q</mi><mi>f</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">q_f</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.7167em; vertical-align: -0.2861em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3361em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0359em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right: 0.10764em;\">f</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.2861em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> when the stack becomes empty:<ul data-start=\"865\" data-end=\"1102\"><li data-start=\"865\" data-end=\"1102\">If <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span></span> reaches a configuration where the stack is empty <strong data-start=\"927\" data-end=\"958\">and the input is fully read</strong>, add a transition:\n<span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>q</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>ϵ</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>Z</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>→</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>q</mi><mi>f</mi></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>ϵ</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">(q, \\epsilon, Z_0) \\to (q_f, \\epsilon)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">ϵ</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.07153em;\">Z</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3011em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0715em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">0</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 1.0361em; vertical-align: -0.2861em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3361em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0359em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right: 0.10764em;\">f</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.2861em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">ϵ</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span>\nThis transition moves to <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>q</mi><mi>f</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">q_f</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.7167em; vertical-align: -0.2861em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3361em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0359em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right: 0.10764em;\">f</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.2861em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> when the stack is empty.</li></ul></li><li data-start=\"1103\" data-end=\"1177\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>q</mi><mi>f</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">q_f</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.7167em; vertical-align: -0.2861em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3361em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0359em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right: 0.10764em;\">f</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.2861em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> is now the <strong data-start=\"1126\" data-end=\"1146\">only final state</strong>, and we accept if we reach it.</li></ul><h3 data-start=\"1179\" data-end=\"1204\"><strong data-start=\"1183\" data-end=\"1202\">Why This Works:</strong></h3><ul data-start=\"1205\" data-end=\"1463\"><li data-start=\"1205\" data-end=\"1334\">Since the original PDA accepted by empty stack, this transition ensures we accept exactly when the stack would have been empty.</li><li data-start=\"1335\" data-end=\"1463\">Now, instead of checking for an empty stack, we just check if we reach <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>q</mi><mi>f</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">q_f</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.7167em; vertical-align: -0.2861em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3361em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0359em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right: 0.10764em;\">f</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.2861em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>, making it a PDA with final state acceptance.</li></ul><hr data-start=\"1465\" data-end=\"1468\"><h2 data-start=\"1470\" data-end=\"1559\"><strong data-start=\"1473\" data-end=\"1557\">2. Converting PDA with Final State Acceptance to PDA with Empty Stack Acceptance</strong></h2><h3 data-start=\"1560\" data-end=\"1575\"><strong data-start=\"1564\" data-end=\"1573\">Idea:</strong></h3><p data-start=\"1576\" data-end=\"1704\">We modify the PDA so that when it reaches a <strong data-start=\"1620\" data-end=\"1635\">final state</strong>, it ensures the stack is empty by \"forcing\" the stack to be cleared.</p><h3 data-start=\"1706\" data-end=\"1729\"><strong data-start=\"1710\" data-end=\"1727\">Construction:</strong></h3><ul data-start=\"1730\" data-end=\"2341\"><li data-start=\"1730\" data-end=\"1826\">Let <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>Q</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Σ</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Γ</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>δ</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>q</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>Z</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P = (Q, \\Sigma, \\Gamma, \\delta, q_0, Z_0, F)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.13889em;\">P</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Q</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">Σ</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">Γ</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03785em;\">δ</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3011em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0359em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">0</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.07153em;\">Z</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3011em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0715em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">0</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span> be a PDA that accepts by final state.</li><li data-start=\"1827\" data-end=\"1906\">Introduce a <strong data-start=\"1841\" data-end=\"1870\">new start state <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>q</mi><mi>s</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">q_s</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.625em; vertical-align: -0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.1514em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0359em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">s</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong> and a <strong data-start=\"1877\" data-end=\"1905\">new stack symbol <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>X</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">X</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.07847em;\">X</span></span></span></span></strong>.</li><li data-start=\"1907\" data-end=\"2341\">Modify the PDA as follows:<ol data-start=\"1938\" data-end=\"2341\"><li data-start=\"1938\" data-end=\"2069\"><strong data-start=\"1941\" data-end=\"2006\">Before starting the original PDA, push <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>X</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">X</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.07847em;\">X</span></span></span></span> onto the stack</strong>:\n<span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>q</mi><mi>s</mi></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>ϵ</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>ϵ</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>→</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>q</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>X</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">(q_s, \\epsilon, \\epsilon) \\to (q_0, X)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.1514em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0359em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">s</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">ϵ</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">ϵ</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3011em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0359em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">0</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.07847em;\">X</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span></li><li data-start=\"2072\" data-end=\"2341\"><strong data-start=\"2075\" data-end=\"2144\">If <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span></span> reaches a final state <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>q</mi><mi>f</mi></msub><mo>∈</mo><mi>F</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">q_f \\in F</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.8252em; vertical-align: -0.2861em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3361em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0359em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right: 0.10764em;\">f</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.2861em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">∈</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.13889em;\">F</span></span></span></span>, clear the stack</strong>:<ul data-start=\"2151\" data-end=\"2341\"><li data-start=\"2151\" data-end=\"2285\">Add a transition that pops everything when <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>q</mi><mi>f</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">q_f</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.7167em; vertical-align: -0.2861em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3361em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0359em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right: 0.10764em;\">f</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.2861em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> is reached:\n<span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>q</mi><mi>f</mi></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>ϵ</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>X</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>→</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>q</mi><mi>f</mi></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>ϵ</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">(q_f, \\epsilon, X) \\to (q_f, \\epsilon)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 1.0361em; vertical-align: -0.2861em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3361em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0359em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right: 0.10764em;\">f</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.2861em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">ϵ</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.07847em;\">X</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 1.0361em; vertical-align: -0.2861em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.03588em;\">q</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.3361em;\"><span style=\"top: -2.55em; margin-left: -0.0359em; margin-right: 0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height: 2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right: 0.10764em;\">f</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">&ZeroWidthSpace;</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height: 0.2861em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right: 0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">ϵ</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span></li><li data-start=\"2291\" data-end=\"2341\">This ensures the stack is empty upon acceptance.</li></ul></li></ol></li></ul><h3 data-start=\"2343\" data-end=\"2368\"><strong data-start=\"2347\" data-end=\"2366\">Why This Works:</strong></h3><ul data-start=\"2369\" data-end=\"2614\"><li data-start=\"2369\" data-end=\"2478\">The extra symbol <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>X</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">X</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height: 0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right: 0.07847em;\">X</span></span></span></span> ensures that <strong data-start=\"2409\" data-end=\"2417\">only</strong> when the PDA reaches a final state can the stack be emptied.</li><li data-start=\"2479\" data-end=\"2614\">Now, instead of checking if the PDA is in a final state, we check if the stack is empty, making it a PDA with empty stack acceptance.</li></ul><hr data-start=\"2616\" data-end=\"2619\"><h2 data-start=\"2621\" data-end=\"2640\"><strong data-start=\"2624\" data-end=\"2638\">Conclusion</strong></h2><ul data-start=\"2641\" data-end=\"2949\"><li data-start=\"2641\" data-end=\"2738\"><strong data-start=\"2643\" data-end=\"2686\">Both types of acceptance are equivalent</strong> because we can construct one type from the other.</li><li data-start=\"2739\" data-end=\"2865\">This proves that <strong data-start=\"2758\" data-end=\"2862\">acceptance by empty stack and acceptance by final state recognize the same class of languages (CFLs)</strong>.</li><li data-start=\"2866\" data-end=\"2949\">Thus, PDAs accepting by <strong data-start=\"2892\" data-end=\"2946\">empty stack or final state are equivalent in power</strong>.</li></ul><p data-start=\"2951\" data-end=\"3007\" data-is-last-node=\"\">Would you like an example conversion for a specific PDA?</p></div>"
